reviewText: It's worth the money,real recognize real and this is worth the wait because it's definitely real.

This DVD offers to the viewer a fascinating and entertaining story about CHAZ who is 50 cents manager who ran his own record label and is a mobster who robbed and is involved with federal shootouts.  I enjoyed this DVD and recommend it to others.  This DVD arrived within the expected time and I am very happy with the service provided by this seller.
